data.description: With limited inventory available, choose a home with upside equity potential! Lovingly cared-for, wisely updated, and ready to be yours. This cute 3bed/1bath/3car house sits on a spacious 1.93 acre lot in St. Croix Central Schools. Quiet rural setting, and less than 20 minutes to Hudson! Open concept kitchen overlooks the living and dining room, plus the massive back yard with prairie views. Lower level is ready for your equity building opportunity and imagination. Shed on the back of the property is not included with the sale.
